#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an8.6"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.6:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.6:0.2"
msgid "1. Mettāvagga "
msgstr "1. Love "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an8.6:0.3"
msgid "6. Dutiyalokadhammasutta "
msgstr "6. Worldly Conditions (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an8.6:1.1"
msgid "“Aṭṭhime, bhikkhave, lokadhammā lokaṃ anuparivattanti, loko ca aṭṭha lokadhamme anuparivattati. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, the eight worldly conditions revolve around the world, and the world revolves around the eight worldly conditions. "

msgctxt "an8.6:1.2"
msgid "Katame aṭṭha? "
msgstr "What eight? "

msgctxt "an8.6:1.3"
msgid "Lābho ca, alābho ca, yaso ca, ayaso ca, nindā ca, pasaṃsā ca, sukhañca, dukkhañca. "
msgstr "Gain and loss, fame and disgrace, praise and blame, pleasure and pain. "

msgctxt "an8.6:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭha lokadhammā lokaṃ anuparivattanti, loko ca ime aṭṭha lokadhamme anuparivattati. "
msgstr "These eight worldly conditions revolve around the world, and the world revolves around these eight worldly conditions. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.158, sc2
msgctxt "an8.6:2.1"
msgid "Assutavato, bhikkhave, puthujjanassa uppajjati lābhopi alābhopi yasopi ayasopi nindāpi pasaṃsāpi sukhampi dukkhampi. "
msgstr "An uneducated ordinary person encounters gain and loss, fame and disgrace, praise and blame, and pleasure and pain. "

msgctxt "an8.6:2.2"
msgid "Sutavatopi, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa uppajjati lābhopi alābhopi yasopi ayasopi nindāpi pasaṃsāpi sukhampi dukkhampi. "
msgstr "And so does an educated noble disciple. "

#. VAR: adhippayāso → adhippāyo (si) | adhippāyaso (s1-3, km) | adhippāyoso (pts1)
msgctxt "an8.6:2.3"
msgid "Tatra, bhikkhave, ko viseso ko adhippayāso kiṃ nānākaraṇaṃ sutavato ariyasāvakassa assutavatā puthujjanenā”ti? "
msgstr "What, then, is the difference between an ordinary uneducated person and an educated noble disciple?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.6:2.4"
msgid "“Bhagavaṃmūlakā no, bhante, dhammā bhagavaṃnettikā bhagavaṃpaṭisaraṇā. Sādhu vata, bhante, bhagavantaṃyeva paṭibhātu etassa bhāsitassa attho. Bhagavato sutvā bhikkhū dhāressantī”ti. "
msgstr "“Our teachings are rooted in the Buddha. He is our guide and our refuge. Sir, may the Buddha himself please clarify the meaning of this. The mendicants will listen and remember it.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an8.6:3.1"
msgid "“Tena hi, bhikkhave, suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasi karotha, bhāsissāmī”ti. "
msgstr "“Well then, mendicants, listen and pay close attention, I will speak.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.6:3.2"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. "
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” they replied. "

msgctxt "an8.6:3.3"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "The Buddha said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.6:3.4"
msgid "“assutavato, bhikkhave, puthujjanassa uppajjati lābho. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, an uneducated ordinary person encounters gain. "

msgctxt "an8.6:3.5"
msgid "So na iti paṭisañcikkhati: "
msgstr "They don’t reflect: "

msgctxt "an8.6:3.6"
msgid "‘uppanno kho me ayaṃ lābho; "
msgstr "‘I’ve encountered this gain. "

msgctxt "an8.6:3.7"
msgid "so ca kho anicco dukkho vipariṇāmadhammo’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti. "
msgstr "It’s impermanent, suffering, and perishable.’ They don’t truly understand it. "

msgctxt "an8.6:3.8"
msgid "Uppajjati alābho … pe … "
msgstr "They encounter loss … "

msgctxt "an8.6:3.9"
msgid "uppajjati yaso … "
msgstr "fame … "

msgctxt "an8.6:3.10"
msgid "uppajjati ayaso … "
msgstr "disgrace … "

msgctxt "an8.6:3.11"
msgid "uppajjati nindā … "
msgstr "praise … "

msgctxt "an8.6:3.12"
msgid "uppajjati pasaṃsā … "
msgstr "blame … "

msgctxt "an8.6:3.13"
msgid "uppajjati sukhaṃ … "
msgstr "pleasure … "

msgctxt "an8.6:3.14"
msgid "uppajjati dukkhaṃ. "
msgstr "pain. "

msgctxt "an8.6:3.15"
msgid "So na iti paṭisañcikkhati: "
msgstr "They don’t reflect: "

msgctxt "an8.6:3.16"
msgid "‘uppannaṃ kho me idaṃ dukkhaṃ; "
msgstr "‘I’ve encountered this pain. "

msgctxt "an8.6:3.17"
msgid "tañca kho aniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vipariṇāmadhamman’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti. "
msgstr "It’s impermanent, suffering, and perishable.’ They don’t truly understand it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an8.6:4.1"
msgid "Tassa lābhopi cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhati, alābhopi cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhati, yasopi cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhati, ayasopi cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhati, nindāpi cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhati, pasaṃsāpi cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhati, sukhampi cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhati, dukkhampi cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhati. "
msgstr "So gain and loss, fame and disgrace, praise and blame, and pleasure and pain occupy their mind. "

msgctxt "an8.6:4.2"
msgid "So uppannaṃ lābhaṃ anurujjhati, alābhe paṭivirujjhati; "
msgstr "They favor gain and oppose loss. "

msgctxt "an8.6:4.3"
msgid "uppannaṃ yasaṃ anurujjhati, ayase paṭivirujjhati; "
msgstr "They favor fame and oppose disgrace. "

msgctxt "an8.6:4.4"
msgid "uppannaṃ pasaṃsaṃ anurujjhati, nindāya paṭivirujjhati; "
msgstr "They favor praise and oppose blame. "

msgctxt "an8.6:4.5"
msgid "uppannaṃ sukhaṃ anurujjhati, dukkhe paṭivirujjhati. "
msgstr "They favor pleasure and oppose pain. "

msgctxt "an8.6:4.6"
msgid "So evaṃ anurodhavirodhasamāpanno na parimuccati jātiyā jarāya maraṇena sokehi paridevehi dukkhehi domanassehi upāyāsehi. "
msgstr "Being so full of favoring and opposing, they’re not freed from rebirth, old age, and death, from sorrow, lamentation, pain, sadness, and distress. "

msgctxt "an8.6:4.7"
msgid "‘Na parimuccati dukkhasmā’ti vadāmi. "
msgstr "They’re not freed from suffering, I say. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.159, sc5
msgctxt "an8.6:5.1"
msgid "Sutavato ca kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa uppajjati lābho. "
msgstr "An educated noble disciple encounters gain. "

msgctxt "an8.6:5.2"
msgid "So iti paṭisañcikkhati: "
msgstr "They reflect: "

msgctxt "an8.6:5.3"
msgid "‘uppanno kho me ayaṃ lābho; "
msgstr "‘I’ve encountered this gain. "

msgctxt "an8.6:5.4"
msgid "so ca kho anicco dukkho vipariṇāmadhammo’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. "
msgstr "It’s impermanent, suffering, and perishable.’ They truly understand it. "

msgctxt "an8.6:5.5"
msgid "Uppajjati alābho … pe … "
msgstr "They encounter loss … "

msgctxt "an8.6:5.6"
msgid "uppajjati yaso … "
msgstr "fame … "

msgctxt "an8.6:5.7"
msgid "uppajjati ayaso … "
msgstr "disgrace … "

msgctxt "an8.6:5.8"
msgid "uppajjati nindā … "
msgstr "praise … "

msgctxt "an8.6:5.9"
msgid "uppajjati pasaṃsā … "
msgstr "blame … "

msgctxt "an8.6:5.10"
msgid "uppajjati sukhaṃ … "
msgstr "pleasure … "

msgctxt "an8.6:5.11"
msgid "uppajjati dukkhaṃ. "
msgstr "pain. "

msgctxt "an8.6:5.12"
msgid "So iti paṭisañcikkhati: "
msgstr "They reflect: "

msgctxt "an8.6:5.13"
msgid "‘uppannaṃ kho me idaṃ dukkhaṃ; "
msgstr "‘I’ve encountered this pain. "

msgctxt "an8.6:5.14"
msgid "tañca kho aniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vipariṇāmadhamman’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. "
msgstr "It’s impermanent, suffering, and perishable.’ They truly understand it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an8.6:6.1"
msgid "Tassa lābhopi cittaṃ na pariyādāya tiṭṭhati, alābhopi cittaṃ na pariyādāya tiṭṭhati, yasopi cittaṃ na pariyādāya tiṭṭhati, ayasopi cittaṃ na pariyādāya tiṭṭhati, nindāpi cittaṃ na pariyādāya tiṭṭhati, pasaṃsāpi cittaṃ na pariyādāya tiṭṭhati, sukhampi cittaṃ na pariyādāya tiṭṭhati, dukkhampi cittaṃ na pariyādāya tiṭṭhati. "
msgstr "So gain and loss, fame and disgrace, praise and blame, and pleasure and pain don’t occupy their mind. "

msgctxt "an8.6:6.2"
msgid "So uppannaṃ lābhaṃ nānurujjhati, alābhe nappaṭivirujjhati; "
msgstr "They don’t favor gain or oppose loss. "

msgctxt "an8.6:6.3"
msgid "uppannaṃ yasaṃ nānurujjhati, ayase nappaṭivirujjhati; "
msgstr "They don’t favor fame or oppose disgrace. "

msgctxt "an8.6:6.4"
msgid "uppannaṃ pasaṃsaṃ nānurujjhati, nindāya nappaṭivirujjhati; "
msgstr "They don’t favor praise or oppose blame. "

msgctxt "an8.6:6.5"
msgid "uppannaṃ sukhaṃ nānurujjhati, dukkhe nappaṭivirujjhati. "
msgstr "They don’t favor pleasure or oppose pain. "

msgctxt "an8.6:6.6"
msgid "So evaṃ anurodhavirodhavippahīno parimuccati jātiyā jarāya maraṇena sokehi paridevehi dukkhehi domanassehi upāyāsehi. "
msgstr "Having given up favoring and opposing, they’re freed from rebirth, old age, and death, from sorrow, lamentation, pain, sadness, and distress. "

msgctxt "an8.6:6.7"
msgid "‘Parimuccati dukkhasmā’ti vadāmi. "
msgstr "They’re freed from suffering, I say. "

msgctxt "an8.6:6.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhave, viseso ayaṃ adhippayāso idaṃ nānākaraṇaṃ sutavato ariyasāvakassa assutavatā puthujjanenāti. "
msgstr "This is the difference between an educated noble disciple and an uneducated ordinary person. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an8.6:7.1"
msgid "Lābho alābho ca yasāyaso ca, "
msgstr "Gain and loss, fame and disgrace, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.6:7.2"
msgid "Nindā pasaṃsā ca sukhaṃ dukhañca; "
msgstr "praise and blame, and pleasure and pain. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.6:7.3"
msgid "Ete aniccā manujesu dhammā, "
msgstr "These qualities among people are impermanent, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.6:7.4"
msgid "Asassatā vipariṇāmadhammā. "
msgstr "transient, and perishable. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an8.6:8.1"
msgid "Ete ca ñatvā satimā sumedho, "
msgstr "A clever and mindful person knows these things, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.6:8.2"
msgid "Avekkhati vipariṇāmadhamme; "
msgstr "seeing that they’re perishable. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.6:8.3"
msgid "Iṭṭhassa dhammā na mathenti cittaṃ, "
msgstr "Desirable things don’t disturb their mind, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.6:8.4"
msgid "Aniṭṭhato no paṭighātameti. "
msgstr "nor are they repelled by the undesirable. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.160, sc9
msgctxt "an8.6:9.1"
msgid "Tassānurodhā atha vā virodhā, "
msgstr "Both favoring and opposing "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.6:9.2"
msgid "Vidhūpitā atthaṅgatā na santi; "
msgstr "are cleared and ended, they are no more. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.6:9.3"
msgid "Padañca ñatvā virajaṃ asokaṃ, "
msgstr "Knowing the stainless, sorrowless state, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.6:9.4"
msgid "Sammappajānāti bhavassa pāragū”ti. "
msgstr "they understand rightly, going beyond rebirth.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.6:9.5"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
